timelineItems.text: 2’ - Early corner chance for the Sounders as Kenny forces one on the far side. #SEAvSJ

timelineItems.text: HT - Sounders with another flurry of chances but it’s all square after the first 15 of extra time. #SEAvSJ #imtired

timelineItems.comment: First Half Extra Time ends, Seattle Sounders FC 1, San Jose Earthquakes 1.
Second Half Extra Time begins Seattle Sounders FC 1, San Jose Earthquakes 1.

timelineItems.text: 120’ - This is the last minute. #SEAvSJ

timelineItems.text: My fingers are cramping. #SEAvSJ

timelineItems.name: San Jose Earthquakes
timelineItems.text: Extra time is up! Looks like PKs are going to be the deciding factor in this one: http://t.co/ZUIoOpsEry #SEAvSJ #Quakes74

timelineItems.comment: Penalty Shootout begins Seattle Sounders FC 1, San Jose Earthquakes 1.
Goal!  Seattle Sounders FC 1(1), San Jose Earthquakes 1. Gonzalo Pineda (Seattle Sounders FC) converts the penalty with a left footed shot to the bottom right corner.
Goal!  Seattle Sounders FC 1(1), San Jose Earthquakes 1(1). Khari Stephenson (San Jose Earthquakes) converts the penalty with a right footed shot to the bottom left corner.
Goal!  Seattle Sounders FC 1(2), San Jose Earthquakes 1(1). Marco Pappa (Seattle Sounders FC) converts the penalty with a left footed shot to the bottom right corner.
Goal!  Seattle Sounders FC 1(3), San Jose Earthquakes 1(1). Brad Evans (Seattle Sounders FC) converts the penalty with a right footed shot to the bottom right corner.
Penalty missed! Still  Seattle Sounders FC 1(2), San Jose Earthquakes 1(1). Alan Gordon (San Jose Earthquakes) hits the left post with a right footed shot.
Penalty saved! J.J. Koval (San Jose Earthquakes) fails to capitalise on this great opportunity,  right footed shot saved  in the centre of the goal.
Goal!  Seattle Sounders FC 1(4), San Jose Earthquakes 1(1). Lamar Neagle (Seattle Sounders FC) converts the penalty with a right footed shot to the bottom left corner.

timelineItems.name: San Jose Earthquakes
timelineItems.text: FT: And Neagle seals the deal. @SoundersFC go through to the next round of @usopencup 4-1 on PKs. #SEAvSJ

timelineItems.comment: Penalty Shootout ends, Seattle Sounders FC 1(4), San Jose Earthquakes 1(1).

timelineItems.name: Sounders Matchday
timelineItems.text: 2’ - Pineda scuffs the corner but it ends up get shot back in by Pappa but wide. Still 0-0 hehehe. #SEAvSJ

timelineItems.comment: Match ends, Seattle Sounders FC 1(4), San Jose Earthquakes 1(1).

timelineItems.text: Can we do that again? #USOC2014 #SEAvSJ
